welcome_message_body: Welcome to Coeur d'Alene, where the stunning lake, picturesque downtown, and friendly locals await you. Take in the beauty of the area and immerse yourself in all the charm this city has to offer. Enjoy your stay and explore everything Coeur d'Alene has to offer!
